  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK accounting and audit framework from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Letters to audit firms and companies setting out changes to the UK’s corporate reporting framework from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

